custom-meta.meta-value: The GP consultation data contain confidential information, with public data deposition non-permissible for socioeconomic reasons. The GP consultation data resides with the RCGP Research and Surveillance Centre and are available via the RCGP RSC website ( www.rcgp.org.uk/rsc). All other raw data utilised in this study are publicly available; relevant references and data repositories are stated within the main manuscript and supporting information. Code and processed data used for the study is available at https://github.com/EdMHill/SeasonalFluImmunityPropagation.
